attributes.Long form description: The instructor tells the student how to disassemble a knaverrik piece of furniture. The student loosens and unscrews all of the hex heads and begins disassembling the legs, top table, middle shelf, and the rest of the cabinet's hex heads. The student places the pieces on the table and saves the hex socket heads in a bag.
